===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|yeerly}}, {{m|enm|yerely}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|ġēarlīc||yearly, of the year, annual}}, equivalent to {{suffix|year|ly|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|yerelie||yearly}}, {{cog|stq|jierelk||yearly}}, {{cog|fy|jierliks||yearly}}, {{cog|nl|jaarlijks||yearly}}, {{cog|de|jährlich||yearly}}, {{cog|sv|årlig||yearly}}, {{cog|is|árlegur||yearly}}.

